    "isActivity": false,
    "urn": "urn:li:activity:7437506371471732736",
    "url": "https://www.linkedin.com/posts/jeffevans_id-choose-podcast-ads-over-meta-ads-almost-activity-7437506371471732736-ZBbV?utm_source=combined_share_message&utm_medium=member_desktop&rcm=ACoAACKcI8YBZXZpYrQ5Sh_n3WjQ4z9yqmCEvUo",
    "timeSincePosted": "3d",
    "shareUrn": "urn:li:share:7437473385141547008",
    "text": "I\u2019d choose podcast ads over Meta ads almost every time\n\nHere\u2019s why\u2026\n\nMeta is interruption marketing.\n\nYou're doom scrolling, an ad appears, you click or you don't. There\u2019s barely any relationship between the brand and audience.\n\nPodcast ads work completely differently. The host has spent years earning trust with their audience. So when they recommend your product, it's like a tip from a friend. That's a currency an ad budget can\u2019t buy.\n\nBut the real unlock with podcast ads is the compounding. \n\nA podcast ad lives within an episode forever. You could run a campaign today and wake up a year from now still seeing sales from it, vs. Meta which stops the moment you stop paying.\n\nAnd then when you layer podcast ads on top of Meta; The trust built through podcasts starts lifting your Meta conversion too. \n\nThe returns back it up, 3 to 5x on a well run podcast campaign. But the true advantage is the trust you build in tandem.",
